==English==

===Noun===
'''urine''' ([[uncountable]])

# {{physiology}} Liquid [[excrement]] consisting of [[water]], [[salt]]s and [[urea]], which is made in the [[kidney]]s, stored in the [[bladder]], then released through the [[urethra]].

